Firearm stops in his tracks as he recieves Savanah's transmission, Rex 
crashing into him.

"You heard that?" Firearm asks, as Rex regains his balance. Rex nods. "Let's 
go."

Both bots activate their jetpacks, heading toward Savanah's position.
